# Integration & extensibility

- Web/Mobile: cùng use case; adapters trong infrastructure/presentation/channels.
- Multi-device: version + idempotency; conflict in domain.
- Multi-DB: one port per role; adapters in persistence/.
- 3rd party: infrastructure/external/ + ACL only.

Chi tiết: `extensibility_integration.md`.
